<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #c90431; font-size: 22px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Here&rsquo;s how.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px;"><img src="http://tonyblake.com/TESTsites/honeywell_email/images/HWredline.jpg" alt="" width="650" height="2" /></p>
<p style="margin-top: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">It&rsquo;s the simplest, most powerful rule of business &ndash; if you&rsquo;re selling to a customer, you give &lsquo;em what they want.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">In  the last Honeywell Customer Experience Team email, we shared the  top-three things customers expect from our company. Now, let&rsquo;s take an  in-depth view of what they&rsquo;re looking for.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><strong>Customer Support:</strong> OEM surveys said they wanted immediate attention from someone qualified  to answer their question when they called. So Honeywell completely  rebuilt our technical service call center to eliminate hand-offs and  immediately connect customers with Honeywell experts. We increased the  average tenure of the tech staff from 8-20 years, and provide true 24X7  service.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><strong>Delivery:</strong> To help guide customers through the time and cost intensive period  after taking possession of a new platform, Honeywell created the Entry  Into Service (EIS) Team. A unique offering in the industry, EIS supports  new platform owners with training, operational guidance, and trouble  shooting.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;"><strong>Communication:</strong> Finding information on Service Bulletins (SB) is a painstaking experience,  customers told us. So we&rsquo;re changing that. Instead of sifting through  every SB or RMU currently available for every platform, <a style="color: #c90431; text-decoration: none;" href="http://performanceaccel.honeywell.com" target="_blank">AT&amp;Rs Performance Accelerator</a> automatically searches for and displays information that pertains to the client&rsquo;s fleet.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img src="http://tonyblake.com/TESTsites/honeywell_email/images/HWgrayline.jpg" alt="" width="650" height="2" /></p>
