<td width="471">
<p style="margin-top: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">These  are just some of the things we&rsquo;re doing as a company to meet the  expectations of our best customers. In our next emailing, the Honeywell  Customer Experience team will offer a few suggestions on working with  customers who may not be in the best of moods.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #c90431; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Let us know your needs.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">The Honeywell Customer Experience Team is on your team.</p>
